Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) is another possible sub-category as the paper discusses the implementation of these techniques in mobile apps and digital cameras, which are user-facing technologies. 

Information Retrieval (cs.IR) is a possible sub-category as the paper discusses the use of machine learning techniques for photo quality evaluation, which can be seen as a form of content-based image retrieval. 

Finally, Machine Learning (cs.LG) is a possible sub-category as the paper discusses the use of machine learning techniques for feature extraction and photo quality evaluation.
